{"type": "article", "id": 23932, "title": "1+1+1烛台", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-16T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071045076LfIUcxvGPqB80u5.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组烛台，每一个都可以分解成木质圆柱、金属陀螺和铁质圆环这几个部分。设计师分别来自冰岛、瑞典和芬兰三个国家，他们在一起做了这个有趣的试验，每个人设计一个部分，事先并不知道别人的材料和形状，最后凑在一起可以组成 27 种，让这组烛台本身增加了趣味性。<a href=\"http://www.1plus1plus1.net/candle-holders/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071045054BVzaWNXPChgrbwm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104505lMtphzWRqu4ONCY9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104506rmLIa8Yu9RhcG7sy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104507ZBn8SAv51gaOysh0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}